text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This transmits obsolete IRM 1.18.1, Distribution, Mission of Distribution.
The material previously contained in IRM 1.18.1, Distribution, Mission of Distribution, is incorporated into IRM 1.1.13.7.4.5, Distribution, dated October 7, 2013.
Former IRM 1.18.1.4, Government Program Management Office, has been discontinued.
IRM 1.18.1 dated September 25, 2006 is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal.
